Title: 027: Career Choice, Disruptions in Finance and Application Stacks with Aziz Mamatov
Description:
In this episode of the SuperDataScience Podcast, I chat with Vice President of Finance Aziz Mamatov. You will get advice on how to choose a career, learn about the disruptions in the financial industry landscape and get to know about application stacks.


If you enjoyed this episode, check out show notes, resources, and more at www.superdatascience.com/27
